skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
Life can be complicated. It can be simple. It can be happy or sad. Today as it was thousands of years ago. Now, the human experience has in some ways changed but in many ways it has stayed pretty much the same. 
This skill tells many things we can learn and apply to our lives from the wisest people who have been here before us.
